### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Smart connect
POST http://localhost:3000/ai/smart-connect
Authorization: Bearer <FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device": "ios",
  "device_id": "abc123"
}
# Response: { session_id, server, wg_config { provider, endpoint, peer_public_key, private_key, allowed_ips, dns }, expires_at }

### Metrics
GET http://localhost:3000/servers/metrics

### Heartbeat
POST http://localhost:3000/connection/heartbeat
Authorization: Bearer <FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "session123",
  "status": "connected",
  "local_ping_ms": 70
}

### Admin metrics
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/metrics
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "USA": { "latency_ms": 100, "load_percent": 30, "stability": 90 },
  "RWANDA": { "latency_ms": 40, "load_percent": 60, "stability": 95 },
  "updated_at": ""
}
